akademikList.name: Dom Studenta Nr 1 „Muchomorek”
akademikList.details: For students of the University of Warsaw and scholarship holders of the PAFF and UW Foundation, MOST and Erasmus programs, the dormitory deposit is in the amount of one month's fee. Deposits in the amount of two-month dormitory fees are for students of other universities.

akademikList.name: Student Depot Warszawa
akademikList.details: Premium Student dorm with high quality conditions and international atmosphere. Located in the green surroundings of Mokotow, nearby the public transport stops, with great communication with the main Warsaw schools and the city centre.
